This paper involves natural language processing and statistical analysis of literature and microarray data to identify potential protein-protein interactions. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), databases (cs.DB), and computational biology and bioinformatics (cs.CE).
